==== Change logs ====
02/14/2020 v1.6.0 - `searchSprintsInSIM` to search sprints in SIM during last `SPRINT_STARTDATE` days
01/30/2020 v1.5.0 - `convertId` to encrypt/decrypt amazon_id - `searchCodePackage` to replace current `searchPackage` - `searchCodeVersionSets` to replace current `SearchVersionSets` - add `--insecure` in curl to fix `sage` request chhetty@
09/14/2018 v1.4.1 - fix cr bug @lunanton
09/14/2018 v1.4.0 - "wiki" to search wiki only - "mwiki" to search wiki recently updated by yourself
08/28/2018 v1.3.0 - Add "Add favorite pipelines". When searching packages, you can add it to favorite packages by pressing "cmd+enter"
08/28/2018 v1.2.1 - Set up a new api for collecting data
08/22/2018 - Add "Search Owned Apollo Env by yourself" with prefix "oap"(owned apollo) with optional query - Add "Search Apollo Env By Prefix" with prefix "ap"
08/14/2018 - Add "Search wikis recently updated" with prefix "wiki" with optional query - Add "Search SIMs recently commented" with prefix "sim" with optional query - Add "Add favorite packages". When searching packages, you can add it to favorite packages by pressing "alt+enter" - Add "Remove favorite packages". When searching favorite packages using "mpk", you can remove it from list by pressing "alt+enter" - Append mpk with optional query - Add SHARE_DATA option for user to control the data sharing - If share data to tools' owner, use sha1 to encrypt the args in sharing data for personal privacy.
07/26/2018 - Add "Search favorite packages..." Feature with prefix "mpk" (my packages) in code.amazon.com - Update curl with auth & headers - Update golang & brazilmakego version - Update CR with CRUX
02/10/2017 - Limit LDAP search results to 25 to speed up pt(phone tool) search (Thanks to bgrubin@)
02/07/2017 - Add “See more details ..” to the end of is(is.amazon.com) search - package search now open code.amazon.com directly (holding CMD if you want to go to devcentral.amazon.com)
12/21/2016 - Fix “is” search to escape spaces in the query
